Emma Johnson is free for lunch at 12:00 on 2024-05-19. I will now create an event with Sarah Baker.

<function-result>[
    {
        "type": "function",
        "name": "create_event",
        "parameters": {
            "Title": "Lunch",
            "Description": "Catch up over lunch.",
            "StartTime": "2024-05-19T12:00:00",
            "EndTime": "2024-05-19T13:00:00",
            "Participants": [
                "sarah.baker@example.com"
            ]
        },
